1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,065
Welcome to Body-Based Inner Child
Connection.

2
00:00:03,065 --> 00:00:07,792
This practice helps you notice how a
younger part may communicate through body

3
00:00:07,792 --> 00:00:08,406
sensation.

4
00:00:26,406 --> 00:00:26,406
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

5
00:00:26,406 --> 00:00:32,531
You do not need to create a memory. You
do not need to analyze anything. Just

6
00:00:32,531 --> 00:00:34,626
listen gently to the body.

7
00:00:34,626 --> 00:00:37,273
Begin by finding a comfortable position.

8
00:00:37,273 --> 00:00:40,617
Let your body be supported.

9
00:00:40,617 --> 00:00:42,707
Take a slow breath in.

10
00:00:51,707 --> 00:00:51,707
<break time="3s" />

11
00:00:51,707 --> 00:00:53,425
And let it out.

12
00:00:53,425 --> 00:00:55,701
Now scan your body slowly.

13
00:01:07,701 --> 00:01:07,701
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

14
00:01:07,701 --> 00:01:08,955
Notice your face.

15
00:01:08,955 --> 00:01:10,023
Your jaw.

16
00:01:10,023 --> 00:01:11,277
Your throat.

17
00:01:11,277 --> 00:01:12,392
Your shoulders.

18
00:01:12,392 --> 00:01:13,507
Your chest.

19
00:01:13,507 --> 00:01:14,296
Your stomach.

20
00:01:14,296 --> 00:01:15,225
Your back.

21
00:01:15,225 --> 00:01:16,479
Your hands.

22
00:01:16,479 --> 00:01:17,222
Your legs.

23
00:01:17,222 --> 00:01:18,847
Your feet.

24
00:01:18,847 --> 00:01:21,866
Notice any place that calls your
attention.

25
00:01:21,866 --> 00:01:30,922
It might be tight, heavy, warm, cold,
numb, tingly, restless, or empty.

26
00:01:30,922 --> 00:01:32,408
Just notice.

27
00:01:32,408 --> 00:01:38,120
Now ask: Is there a younger part
connected to this body sensation?

28
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:50,120
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

29
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:52,442
If yes, notice gently.

30
00:01:52,442 --> 00:01:57,132
If no, simply stay with the sensation as
sensation.

31
00:01:57,132 --> 00:02:03,262
Ask the sensation or younger part: What
do you want me to know?

32
00:02:15,262 --> 00:02:15,262
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

33
00:02:15,262 --> 00:02:20,417
Listen for words, images, emotions, or a
subtle sense.

34
00:02:20,417 --> 00:02:23,993
Now ask: How old does this feeling seem?

35
00:02:35,993 --> 00:02:35,993
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

36
00:02:35,993 --> 00:02:38,176
Do not force an answer.

37
00:02:38,176 --> 00:02:43,470
Just notice if an age, season, or life
chapter comes to mind.

38
00:02:43,470 --> 00:02:48,253
Now ask: What did this part need back
then?

39
00:03:00,253 --> 00:03:00,253
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

40
00:03:00,253 --> 00:03:06,357
Maybe comfort, protection, attention,
permission to feel, permission to speak,

41
00:03:06,357 --> 00:03:08,101
or permission to rest.

42
00:03:08,101 --> 00:03:11,956
Now place a hand near the body area if
that feels supportive.

43
00:03:11,956 --> 00:03:17,584
You do not have to touch directly. You
can simply bring warmth or attention

44
00:03:17,584 --> 00:03:18,040
there.

45
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:24,916
Say gently: I notice you. I am listening.
You do not have to speak perfectly. Your

46
00:03:24,916 --> 00:03:28,396
body is allowed to tell the truth slowly.

47
00:03:28,396 --> 00:03:33,876
Now ask: What would help this area feel
even one percent safer?

48
00:03:45,876 --> 00:03:45,876
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

49
00:03:45,876 --> 00:03:51,791
Maybe more breath, more space, a
different posture, a blanket, a boundary,

50
00:03:51,791 --> 00:03:53,817
or a word of reassurance.

51
00:03:53,817 --> 00:03:56,139
Offer one small thing.

52
00:03:56,139 --> 00:03:58,833
Now notice whether the sensation changes.

53
00:03:58,833 --> 00:04:05,567
It may soften. It may become stronger. It
may move. It may stay the same.

54
00:04:05,567 --> 00:04:08,168
All responses are allowed.

55
00:04:08,168 --> 00:04:13,897
Now ask the younger part: What do you
want me to carry forward from this

56
00:04:13,897 --> 00:04:14,623
practice?

57
00:04:26,623 --> 00:04:26,623
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

58
00:04:26,623 --> 00:04:27,830
Listen.

59
00:04:45,830 --> 00:04:45,830
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

60
00:04:45,830 --> 00:04:47,130
Thank the body.

61
00:04:47,130 --> 00:04:49,080
Thank the younger part.

62
00:04:49,080 --> 00:04:52,609
Thank any protectors that allowed this
much contact.

63
00:04:52,609 --> 00:04:54,559
Take a slow breath in.

64
00:05:03,559 --> 00:05:03,559
<break time="3s" />

65
00:05:03,559 --> 00:05:04,813
And let it out.

66
00:05:04,813 --> 00:05:07,181
Return your attention to the room.

67
00:05:07,181 --> 00:05:09,596
Notice what you can see.

68
00:05:09,596 --> 00:05:13,497
Notice the ground or support beneath you.

69
00:05:13,497 --> 00:05:16,469
When you are ready, gently return.

